rComments: Incredibly, incredibly nice person, and very easy class.  If you try at all you will definitely get an A, and if you are fairly competent you can easily get an A+.  Didn't learn much because the class was taught as if it was high school / ESL level, but it was nice to not have to stress out about this class.  Two group projects at end of year.
The course is easy and interesting.
Very kind teacher. Very easy homework
